Ai Photo Translator
Ai Photo Translator is a powerful mobile application that leverages advanced machine learning and optical character recognition (OCR) technology to instantly translate text from images. This app enables users to take photos of text in different languages and provides an immediate translation, making it a versatile tool for travelers, language learners, and professionals working in multicultural environments.

Features:
Instant Image Translation: Take photos of text in any language and receive an immediate translation.
Multi-language Support: Supports a wide range of languages for both text input and translation.
User-Friendly Interface: Simple and intuitive design, ensuring a seamless user experience.
Offline Translation: Allows offline translations, making it useful in areas with no internet connection.
Feel free to adjust the description based on additional features and specifics about the app.
